        print(f'   p_value {col}  yield_kg:', correlation, p_value)
        
        
        coefficients = np.polyfit(df1[col], df1['yield_kg'], 1)
        y1 = np.polyval(coefficients, df1[col])
        
        coefficients = np.polyfit(df1[col], df1['yield_kg'], 2)
        y2 = np.polyval(coefficients, df1[col])
        
        coefficients = np.polyfit(df1[col], df1['yield_kg'], 3)
        y3 = np.polyval(coefficients, df1[col])
        
        coefficients = np.polyfit(df1[col], df1['yield_kg'], 4)
        y4 = np.polyval(coefficients, df1[col])

threshold = np.linspace(0, 1, num=101)

true_labels = y_test
predicted_probabilities = model_cl.predict_proba(X_test_final)[:,1]
precision_graph = []


precision_max = 0
thr_max = 0
recall_max = 0

for thr in threshold:
    predicted_labels = [1 if prob >= thr else 0 for prob in predicted_probabilities]
    precision = precision_score(true_labels, predicted_labels)
    precision_graph.append(precision)
    recall = recall_score(true_labels, predicted_labels)
    if precision > precision_max:
        precision_max = precision
        thr_max = thr
        recall_max = recall

print("Precision max:", precision_max);
print('Threshold:', thr_max);
print("Recall:", recall_max);
print()

X_test_num = scaler_cl.transform(X_test[num_col])
X_train_num_df = pd.DataFrame(X_train_num, columns=num_col)
X_test_num_df = pd.DataFrame(X_test_num, columns=num_col)


encoder_cl = OneHotEncoder(drop='first')
X_train_cat = encoder_cl.fit_transform(X_train[cat_col]).toarray()
X_test_cat = encoder_cl.transform(X_test[cat_col]).toarray()
X_train_cat_df = pd.DataFrame(X_train_cat, columns=encoder_cl.get_feature_names(cat_col))
X_test_cat_df = pd.DataFrame(X_test_cat, columns=encoder_cl.get_feature_names(cat_col))


X_train_final = pd.concat([X_train_num_df, X_train_cat_df], axis=1)
X_test_final = pd.concat([X_test_num_df, X_test_cat_df], axis=1)


model_cl = LogisticRegression()
model_cl.fit(X_train_final, y_train)
predictions_cl = model_cl.predict(X_test_final)

In[60]:
threshold = np.linspace(0, 1, num=101)

true_labels = y_test
predicted_probabilities = model_cl.predict_proba(X_test_final)[:,1]
precision_graph = []


precision_max = 0
thr_max = 0
recall_max = 0

for thr in threshold:
    predicted_labels = [1 if prob >= thr else 0 for prob in predicted_probabilities]
    precision = precision_score(true_labels, predicted_labels)
    precision_graph.append(precision)
    recall = recall_score(true_labels, predicted_labels)
    if precision > precision_max:
        precision_max = precision
        thr_max = thr
        recall_max = recall

print("Precision max:", precision_max)
print('Threshold:', thr_max)
print("Recall:", recall_max)
print()
    

plt.plot(threshold, precision_graph)
plt.xlabel('threshold')
plt.ylabel('precision')
plt.grid(True)
